==History== The Carlo Besta Neurological Institute was founded in 1918.<ref name="about">http://www.istituto-besta.com/The-Institute.aspx?doc=Introduction</ref> In 1981 the Italian government designated it as an Institute of Research and Treatment (IRCCS).<ref name="about"/>
==Activities== The Carlo Besta Neurological Institute is a member of [[EuroBioBank]]'s [[biobank]] program.
