The '''Graduate School of Health Economics and Management''' ({{lang-it|Alta Scuola di Economia e Management dei Sistemi Sanitari}}, or '''ALTEMS''') is a [[graduate school]] at the [[Università Cattolica del Sacro Cuore]] established in 2008.<ref>http://wn.com/The_Postgraduate_Schools_System__Università_Cattolica_del_Sacro_Cuore</ref>
